ime":"2019-05-29T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242daea1d2797f9eb7a56394e4384707ce7eb4b5","tid":1175794,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:14:29.000Z","msg":"睇完頭7個字，結論：抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489d07278f2278f6cea1fa035251d652c94ef4c8","tid":1175794,"uid":171082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"242daea1d2797f9eb7a56394e4384707ce7eb4b5","tid":1175794,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:14:29.000Z","msg":"睇完頭7個字，結論：抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:20:53.000Z","msg":"支那雞真係只可屌不可娶....<br />\n我都想安慰樓主但真係唔知講咩好<br />\n下一步就係離婚分身家。。。"},{"pid":"2bcea0c640bf96a6028eea608efbd11eeb8e5073","tid":1175794,"uid":71096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:29:30.000Z","msg":"大６而家邊有３從４得既女人？樓主你為左一時之快，中計了。老實講，趁而家所有支產過晒俾你媽先啦，唔係佢有排同你計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}